sql:
SELECT
  i.i_item_id,
  AVG(ss.ss_quantity) AS agg1,
  AVG(ss.ss_list_price) AS agg2,
  AVG(ss.ss_coupon_amt) AS agg3,
  AVG(ss.ss_sales_price) AS agg4
FROM store_sales AS ss,
  customer_demographics AS cd,
  date_dim AS dd,
  item AS i,
  promotion AS p
WHERE
  ss.ss_sold_date_sk = dd.d_date_sk AND ss.ss_item_sk = i.i_item_sk AND ss.ss_cdemo_sk = cd.cd_demo_sk AND ss.ss_promo_sk = p.p_promo_sk AND cd.cd_gender = 'F' AND cd.cd_marital_status = 'U' AND cd.cd_education_status = '4 yr Degree' AND (p.p_channel_email = 'N' OR p.p_channel_event = 'N') AND dd.d_year = 1998
GROUP BY
  i.i_item_id
ORDER BY
  i.i_item_id
LIMIT 100;
